Package: OPSRtools
Title: Tools for OPSR
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Daniel", "Heimgartner", email = "d.heimgartners@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0643-8690"))
Description: OPSR estimates ordered probit switching regression models - a Heckman
    type endogenous switching regression model with an ordinal selection/treatment 
    and continuous outcomes. OPSRtools contains estimation and post-estimation 
    routines such as step-wise model selection, k-fold cross-validation, treatment 
    effect computations and some visualizations.
